      "message": "I don\u0027t think so.  Pending time should be essentially zero, so to try to make the distinction on Status/whatever doesn\u0027t make a lot of sense when the update interval is a minute or so.  Also, I don\u0027t think we get pubsub messages for \"okay, I actually added the task to the queue.\", ie. nil -\u003e PENDING.  I think the ones causing all of the errors are the PENDING-\u003eRUNNING when the task gets picked up before we\u0027re done triggering a bunch of tasks.",
